-- Telkom Offers Voluntary Severance, Retirement Packages, Business Day Says
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2011-02-10T05:03:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-10/telkom-offers-voluntary-severance-retirement-packages-business-day-says.html
Telkom South Africa Ltd. proposed
voluntary severance and early retirement packages to employees
in a bid to reduce costs, Business Day said, citing labor
unions.  Labor unions will brief their members on the proposal and
report back to Telkom on the outcome, the Johannesburg-based
newspaper said, citing the Solidarity and  Communication Workers
Union .  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
